spx.packets.tracks

Class Threat

  • java.lang.Object
    • spx.packets.tracks.Threat

  • public class Threat
extends java.lang.Object
    Threat information.

    The Threat structure is contained within the extended track report structure.

    This class is kept in sync with the C++ SPxPacketTrackThreat structure in "SPxPackets.h".

    See Also:
    Extended
